; Coverage test for item.cc get_depth returning 0L (L350-351) and lookup
; switch break statements for various function name prefixes (L465, L520,
; L525, L530 and others).
; Accessing parent.X fields triggers xact_t::lookup which falls through
; to item_t::lookup for most names.

2024/01/01 * Cleared Transaction
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 ! Pending Transaction
    Expenses:Rent    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/03 Uncleared Transaction
    Expenses:Gas     $30.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(parent.depth)|%(parent.L)|%(parent.X)|%(parent.Y)|%(account)\n"
0|true|true|false|Expenses:Food
0|true|true|false|Assets:Cash
0|true|false|true|Expenses:Rent
0|true|false|true|Assets:Cash
0|true|false|false|Expenses:Gas
0|true|false|false|Assets:Cash
end test
